{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4243051a8d","title":"拟公布美军细菌战战厚供词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f863fb8d26","index":0,"year":1953,"month":11,"day":8,"articleId":"4243051a8d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"752cfe7754","type":"title","text":"拟公布美军细菌战战停供词","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4243051a8d"},{"id":"1029d1f6f0","type":"paragraph","text":"金首相：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4243051a8d"},{"id":"791426cd10","type":"paragraph","text":"美国最近在联合国大会就细菌战问题重起风波，远我以酷刑逼细菌战仔造假供状。我们拟将美细菌战停十九人供词公布，并在公布之前，以朝鲜人民军总政治局和中国人民志愿军政治部名义发表关于这十九份供词的公报。公报、供词、录音及各厚照片均将于十一月九日以飞机送平壤。我们拟于十一月十日上午北京时间十一时将公报广播，十一日见报。自十一日起连续广播各仔口供并连续在广播后之次日见报。拟请平亦照此日程公布上项公报和供词。以上各点均请电告您的意见。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4243051a8d"},{"id":"33bea34104","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4243051a8d"},{"id":"d6142a3e40","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五三年十一月八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4243051a8d"},{"id":"eb514db91b","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这是毛泽东给朝鲜民主主义人民共和国首相金日成的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4243051a8d"}],"page":{"id":"88c0030a0f","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"4243051a8d","start":431,"end":431}}}},"__N_SSG":true}